CatDescriptText: There is a broadside posted on the building behind the man, reading "[L. Jones] Representative of the Watchtower Society -  Sun., June 15th, at 4 p.m. - Kingdom Hall, 2010 Wylie Avenue, Pittsburgh, PA - You are Invited to Attend - All Welcome - No Collection"
TitMainTitle: Man squatting with little dog on sidewalk, with Royal Crown Cola advertisement on building behind him
